Chapter 10: Service Advertising and Discovery with UDDI

The two utilities in this chapter demonstrate basic UDDI principles while also
introducing the usage of the UDDI::Lite classes from the SOAP::Lite package.
They are (with example and line number references):

biz_by_initial.pl (example 10-6, page 232)
show_biz.pl (shown only in fragments, starting on page 234)
